Module chav1961.purelib
Package chav1961.purelib.streams.char2byte

Class CompilerUtils

java.lang.Object
chav1961.purelib.streams.char2byte.CompilerUtils
public class CompilerUtils
extends java.lang.Object

This class contains a lot of useful methods to use in the wide range of compilers. In conjunction with AsmWriter, it allows to build class, field and method signatures, construct methods calls, getting and setting class and instance fields and so on.

Since:
0.0.3
Author:
Alexander Chernomyrdin aka chav1961
See Also:
Class, Field, Method, Constructor, AsmWriter, JUnit tests
